Market Exchange Rates
BEIJING , February 27 ( Xinhua ) -- The People 's Bank of China today issued the market exchange rates in RMB yuan against three major currencies .
The middle price of RMB against convertible currencies is mainly based on the closing price of the preceding interbank trading .
The designated foreign exchange trading banks will decide the exchange rates in RMB yuan against other convertible currencies according to the tone of the international exchange market and the rules of the People 's Bank of China .
